## 4. Phase plan (meta novel-drug lifecycle)

- **Phase α (entry, this cycle 109)**: meta-roadmap + 5-axis representative + cross-axis lifecycle land.
- **Phase β (per-axis novel drug pilot)**: each axis 의 첫 novel drug 시도.
  - QUANTUM: hxq-ca-krs-001 / hxq-al-ar-001 / hxq-mi-hmg-001 / hxq-ln-tgf-001 / hxq-gen-001 build + VQE (Phase B in `.roadmap.novel_drugs`)
  - WEAVE: novel scaffold + drug payload smoke
  - VIROCAPSID: novel mRNA-LNP encapsulation
  - RIBOZYME: novel ribozyme variant kinetics
  - NANOBOT: novel nanobot release pilot
- **Phase γ (Stage 1-6 lifecycle pilot)**: 단일 novel drug (예: hxq-ca-krs-001) 의 5-axis 전체 lifecycle 검증.
- **Phase δ (cross-axis ranking + lead opt)**: lifecycle PASS 의 novel drug ranking + iterative refinement.

