## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **representative falsifier 는 entry skeleton** — 진정한 evidence 는 axis-specific work (`.roadmap.novel_drugs` Phase B/C/D + 4 disease roadmaps + per-axis roadmap) 에서 land.
2. **5-axis 통합 lifecycle 은 in-silico only** — Stage 3-4 (delivery / mechanism validation) 의 진정한 evidence 는 wet-lab; 본 hexa-bio scope 는 in-silico 가설 검증만.
3. **신규 약물 기준** = de novo design lifecycle 우선; 기존 FDA 약물 검증은 `.roadmap.fda_drug_verification` 의 historical record.
4. **sister-repo cross-bridge** = sim-universe (multiverse bio-variant) + anima (bio-Φ) + nexus (216-lens) + qmirror (cond.14 chemistry/VQE) — 이미 8/8 land (cycles 79-106).
5. **Phase γ pilot 의 진정한 의미** = 단일 novel drug 의 5-axis end-to-end pilot — quantum binding + delivery + mechanism + disease phenotype + ranking 모두 통과.

